<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0386a" n="0386a"/>
<lb n="0386a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0386a02"/><head type="no">No. 161 [No. 152(10)]</head>
<lb n="0386a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0386001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋長壽【元】【明】</note><app n="0386001"><lem>長壽</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說長壽</rdg></app>王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0386a04"/>
<lb n="0386a05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0386002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僧祐…西晉錄＝失譯【宋】，開元錄云安祐二錄並失譯師今附西晉第二出【元】【明】</note><note n="0386002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僧祐…西晉錄＝失譯【宋】，＝開元錄云安祐二錄並失譯師今附西晉第二出【元】【明】</note><app n="0386002" word-count="16"><lem>僧祐錄云安公失譯經人名今附西晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">開元錄云安祐二錄並失譯師今附西晉第二出</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0386a06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0386a07"/><note n="0386003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝爾【明】</note><app n="0386003"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">爾</rdg></app>時佛告諸比丘。<note n="0386004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昔＋（者）【三】</note><note n="0386004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">昔＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386004"><lem>昔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">昔者</rdg></app>有菩薩為大國王。名
<lb n="0386a08"/>曰長壽。王有太子。名曰長生。王<note n="0386005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">治國以政＝以正法治國無【三】</note><note n="0386005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">治國以政＝以正法治國無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386005"><lem>治國以
<lb n="0386a09"/>政</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">以正法治國無</rdg></app>。刀杖之惱不加吏民。風雨時節五穀豐
<lb n="0386a10"/><note n="0386006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熟＝饒【三】</note><note n="0386006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熟＝饒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386006"><lem>熟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">饒</rdg></app>。有&CB00444;國王治行暴虐。不修正<note n="0386007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">治＝法【三】</note><note n="0386007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">治＝法【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386007"><lem>治</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>國民貧
<lb n="0386a11"/>困。謂傍臣曰。我聞長壽王國去是不遠。熾
<lb n="0386a12"/>饒<note n="0386008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">豐＝富【三】</note><note n="0386008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">豐＝富【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386008"><lem>豐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">富</rdg></app>樂而無兵革之備。我欲<note n="0386009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往彼＝今往【三】</note><note n="0386009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">往彼＝今往【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386009"><lem>往彼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">今往</rdg></app>攻奪其
<lb n="0386a13"/>國。為可得不。傍臣對曰。大善。遂興兵而
<lb n="0386a14"/><note n="0386010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝來【三】</note><note n="0386010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝來【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386010"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">來</rdg></app>到長壽王國界。界上吏民走行白王<note n="0386011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】</note><note n="0386011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386011"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0386a15"/>彼貪王興兵而來。欲攻明王之國。<note n="0386012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯願備豫＝惟願豫願【三】</note><note n="0386012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯願備豫＝惟願豫願【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386012"><lem>唯願備
<lb n="0386a16"/>豫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惟願豫願</rdg></app>。長壽王<note n="0386013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">召其＝即召【三】</note><note n="0386013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">召其＝即召【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386013"><lem>召其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">即召</rdg></app>群臣而告之曰。<note n="0386014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝子【宋】</note><app n="0386014"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">子</rdg></app>所以來
<lb n="0386a17"/>者。但貪我國人民倉穀珍寶耳。若與其戰必
<lb n="0386a18"/><note n="0386015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傷＋（害）【三】</note><note n="0386015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">傷＋（害）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386015"><lem>傷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">傷害</rdg></app>吾民。夫諍國殺民。吾不為也。群臣曰。
<lb n="0386a19"/>臣等皆曉習戰法必能勝彼。不使明王之兵
<lb n="0386a20"/>為彼所侵也。王曰。若我勝彼即有死傷。彼
<lb n="0386a21"/>兵我民俱惜壽命。愛我害彼賢者不為也。群
<lb n="0386a22"/>臣不聽。留王於宮。乃自相與於外發兵。出往
<lb n="0386a23"/>界上逆而<note n="0386016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">距＝拒【三】＊</note><note n="0386016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">距＝拒【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0386016"><lem>距</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">拒</rdg></app>之。<note n="0386017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">長壽王…太子＝王告太子長生【三】</note><note n="0386017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">長壽王…太子＝王告太子長生【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386017" word-count="8"><lem>長壽王乃謂其太子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王告太子長生</rdg></app>曰。<note n="0386018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔彼貪我國故來攻我〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386018"><lem>彼
<lb n="0386a24"/>貪我國故來攻我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。今群臣以我故欲逆<note n="0386019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【三】</note><note n="0386019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔而〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386019"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0386a25"/><app type="＊" source="0386016"><lem>距</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">拒</rdg></app>之。夫兩敵相向必有缺傷。今欲與汝俱
<lb n="0386a26"/>委國亡去。太子<note n="0386020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝曰【三】＊</note><note n="0386020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝曰【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0386020"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>諾。即父子<note n="0386021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔共〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386021"><lem>共</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>踰城而出。
<lb n="0386a27"/>幽隱山間</p>
<lb n="0386a28"/><p>於是貪王遂入其國。募求長壽王金千斤錢
<lb n="0386a29"/>千<note n="0386022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬＋（雖能得者）【三】</note><note n="0386022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬＋（雖能得者）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386022"><lem>萬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">萬雖能得者</rdg></app>。長壽王後日出於道邊樹下坐。有遠
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0386b" n="0386b"/>
<lb n="0386b01"/>方婆羅門來。亦息於樹下。問長壽王曰。卿
<lb n="0386b02"/>何處人何緣在此。王曰。我此國中人<note n="0386023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0386023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386023"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。偶
<lb n="0386b03"/>來到此戲耳。長壽王問<note n="0386024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆羅門＋（曰）【三】</note><note n="0386024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆羅門＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386024"><lem>婆羅門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婆羅門曰</rdg></app>。賢者從何
<lb n="0386b04"/>所來將欲所<note n="0386025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝至【三】</note><note n="0386025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝至【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386025"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>。婆羅門<app type="＊" source="0386020"><lem>言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曰</rdg></app>。我遠<note n="0386026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">國＝方【三】</note><note n="0386026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">國＝方【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386026"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">方</rdg></app>貧鄙
<lb n="0386b05"/>之道<note n="0386027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＋（也）【元】【明】</note><app n="0386027"><lem>士</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">士也</rdg></app>。遙聞此國長壽王好喜布施<note n="0386028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">周救＝賑極【宋】，賑拯【元】【明】</note><note n="0386028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">周救＝賑極【宋】，＝賑拯【元】【明】</note><app n="0386028"><lem>周救</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">賑極</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">賑拯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0386b06"/>貧<note n="0386029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羸＝窮【三】</note><note n="0386029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羸＝窮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386029"><lem>羸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">窮</rdg></app>。吾故遠來欲從乞&CB00456;用自生活不知王
<lb n="0386b07"/>意於今云何。卿是<note n="0386030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">國＋（中）【三】</note><note n="0386030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">國＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386030"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">國中</rdg></app>人聽聞其意。於今何如
<lb n="0386b08"/>故肯布施不<note n="0386031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也王默自念＝王為【宋】，王默念自念【元】【明】</note><note n="0386031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也王默自念＝王為【宋】，＝王默念自念【元】【明】</note><app n="0386031"><lem>也。王默自念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">王為</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王默念自念</rdg></app>。子用我<note n="0386032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故＝快【三】</note><note n="0386032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故＝快【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386032"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">快</rdg></app>故從
<lb n="0386b09"/>遠來。值我失國到無所得。而當空去甚<note n="0386033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可哀＝哀可【宋】</note><app n="0386033"><lem>可
<lb n="0386b10"/>哀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">哀可</rdg></app>念。於是王乃<note n="0386034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">垂淚＝涕泣【三】</note><note n="0386034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">垂淚＝涕泣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386034"><lem>垂淚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">涕泣</rdg></app>而<note n="0386035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔謂婆羅門〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386035"><lem>謂婆羅門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰。我即
<lb n="0386b11"/>是長壽王也。有他國王前來攻我。我委國<note n="0386036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡＋（來）【三】</note><note n="0386036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亡＋（來）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386036"><lem>
<lb n="0386b12"/>亡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">亡來</rdg></app>隱<note n="0386037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔藏〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386037"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>此間。今<note n="0386038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞〕－【三】</note><note n="0386038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔聞〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386038"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>賢者故來相歸。值我
<lb n="0386b13"/><note n="0386039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空窮＝困乏【三】</note><note n="0386039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">空窮＝困乏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386039"><lem>空窮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">困乏</rdg></app>無以相副。將奈之何。兩人相向哽<note n="0386040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咽＝噎【三】＊</note><note n="0386040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咽＝噎【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0386040"><lem>咽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">噎</rdg></app>
<lb n="0386b14"/><note n="0386041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啼泣＝涕淚【宋】</note><app n="0386041"><lem>啼泣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">涕淚</rdg></app>。王曰。我聞新王<note n="0386042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慕＝募【三】</note><note n="0386042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝募【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386042"><lem>慕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">募</rdg></app>我甚重。卿<note n="0386043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝可取【三】</note><note n="0386043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝可取【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386043"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">可取</rdg></app>我
<lb n="0386b15"/>頭往可得重<note n="0386044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賞＝償【宋】【元】</note><app n="0386044"><lem>賞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">償</rdg></app>。婆羅門<note n="0386045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝言【三】</note><note n="0386045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰＝言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386045"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>。<note n="0386046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（我）＋遙【三】</note><note n="0386046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（我）＋遙【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386046"><lem>遙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">我遙</rdg></app>聞大王周救
<lb n="0386b16"/>一切故來乞&CB00456;。庶得幾微以養餘命。值王失
<lb n="0386b17"/>國自我薄福。今教斷頭不敢承命。王曰。卿
<lb n="0386b18"/>故遠來欲有所得。<note n="0386047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＝值【三】</note><note n="0386047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遇＝值【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386047"><lem>遇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">值</rdg></app>我困<note n="0386048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乏＝窮【三】</note><note n="0386048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乏＝窮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386048"><lem>乏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">窮</rdg></app>。無以相副。且
<lb n="0386b19"/>人生世皆當趣死。<note n="0386049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔吾等當死願〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0386049"><lem>吾等當死。願</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0386050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以身相惠＝以相與【宋】</note><app n="0386050"><lem>以身相惠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">以相與</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0386b20"/>何<note n="0386051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386051"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>辭讓之<note n="0386052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【宋】</note><app n="0386052"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。今若不取後有來者我猶
<lb n="0386b21"/>與之。不如早取<note n="0386053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0386053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386053"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。婆羅門<app type="＊" source="0386020"><lem>言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曰</rdg></app>。我不忍殺
<lb n="0386b22"/>大王。大王。若有弘慈之意必欲殞命以相惠
<lb n="0386b23"/>施者。但當散手相隨去耳。王即隨去到城門
<lb n="0386b24"/><note n="0386054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">外＝前【三】</note><note n="0386054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＝前【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386054"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>。而令縛之以白貪王。王即<note n="0386055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雇＝酬【三】</note><note n="0386055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雇＝酬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386055"><lem>雇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">酬</rdg></app>婆羅門金
<lb n="0386b25"/>錢之賞。遣令還去</p>
<lb n="0386b26"/><p>貪王於是。乃使人於四街道頭燒殺長壽王。
<lb n="0386b27"/>王故群臣白貪王曰。此臣等故君。今<note n="0386056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔當〕－【三】</note><note n="0386056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔當〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386056"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>就
<lb n="0386b28"/>終歿之罪。願得為設微具以遣送之。貪王聽
<lb n="0386b29"/>之。群臣具饌哽<app type="＊" source="0386040"><lem>咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">噎</rdg></app>臨之。人民觀者皆言。王
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0386c" n="0386c"/>
<lb n="0386c01"/>枉死。郭邑草野莫不呼天</p>
<lb n="0386c02"/><p>太子長生時出<note n="0386057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【三】</note><note n="0386057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔在〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386057"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>道邊。聽聞人語知父為貪
<lb n="0386c03"/>王<note n="0386058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝因【明】</note><app n="0386058"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">因</rdg></app>得。乃<note n="0386059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佯＝徉【三】</note><note n="0386059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佯＝徉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386059"><lem>佯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">徉</rdg></app>擔<note n="0386060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樵＋（薪）【三】</note><note n="0386060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樵＋（薪）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386060"><lem>樵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">樵薪</rdg></app>出於市賣之。間鬧人
<lb n="0386c04"/>中當<note n="0386061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔父〕－【元】</note><app n="0386061"><lem>父</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>前<note n="0386062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝立【元】【明】</note><app n="0386062"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">立</rdg></app>。<note n="0386063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔觀見…悲痛〕九字－【宋】</note><app n="0386063" word-count="9"><lem>觀見父當死心中悲<note n="0386064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痛＝疾【元】【明】</note><app n="0386064"><lem>痛</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">疾</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。父
<lb n="0386c05"/>見長生恐其瞋恚為父報怨。父乃仰天<note n="0386065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">太＝歎【三】</note><note n="0386065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">太＝歎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386065"><lem>太</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">歎</rdg></app>息
<lb n="0386c06"/>曰。夫為人子欲為至孝。使汝父<note n="0386066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（樂）＋死【元】【明】</note><app n="0386066"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">樂死</rdg></app>而<note n="0386067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（懷）【元】【明】</note><app n="0386067"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">不懷</rdg></app>
<lb n="0386c07"/><note n="0386068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">太＝憂者【宋】</note><note n="0386068" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA．eva">恨</lem><rdg wit="【大】">太</rdg></app>＝憂者【宋】</note><app n="0386068"><lem>恨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">憂者</rdg></app>慎。<note n="0386069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫＝無【三】</note><note n="0386069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386069"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>為汝<note n="0386070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">父報＝報父【宋】</note><app n="0386070"><lem>父報</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">報父</rdg></app>怨<note n="0386071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也即＝則【三】</note><note n="0386071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也即＝則【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386071"><lem>也。即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>汝父樂死而
<lb n="0386c08"/>不<note n="0386072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憂＋（也）【三】</note><note n="0386072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憂＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386072"><lem>憂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">憂也</rdg></app>。若違父<note n="0386073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（而）【三】</note><note n="0386073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＋（而）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386073"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">言而</rdg></app>行殺他人者。即令汝父死
<lb n="0386c09"/>有餘恨。長生不忍<note n="0386074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝視【三】</note><note n="0386074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝視【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386074"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>其父死。因還入山。長
<lb n="0386c10"/>壽王遂就燒死之誅</p>
<lb n="0386c11"/><p>長生久後<note n="0386075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝思【三】</note><note n="0386075" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＝思【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386075"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">思</rdg></app>念。我父仁義深篤至死不轉
<lb n="0386c12"/>而此貪王無狀不別善惡。枉殺我父。雖我父
<lb n="0386c13"/>有慈惻淳仁之心死而不恚。然我不能忍也。
<lb n="0386c14"/>我不出殺此貪王者。我終不苟生於世矣。遂
<lb n="0386c15"/>出傭賃國中。大臣徇園於市賃人。得長生使
<lb n="0386c16"/>種菜種。菜甚好。後日大臣案行園田。見菜
<lb n="0386c17"/>甚好呼問園監。<note n="0386076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔園〕－【三】</note><note n="0386076" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔園〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386076"><lem>園</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>監對曰。前賃得一人使
<lb n="0386c18"/>為之。故好如是。大臣因呼長生<note n="0386077" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝問【三】</note><note n="0386077" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝問【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386077"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">問</rdg></app>之。<note n="0386078" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔問言〕－【三】</note><note n="0386078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔問言〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386078"><lem>問言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0386c19"/>卿頗能作飲食不<note n="0386079" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耶對〕－【三】</note><note n="0386079" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔耶對〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386079"><lem>耶。對</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰能作。<note n="0386080" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（便）＋使【三】</note><note n="0386080" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（便）＋使【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386080"><lem>使</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">便使</rdg></app>作飲
<lb n="0386c20"/><note n="0386081" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（飲食）【三】</note><note n="0386081" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（飲食）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386081"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">食飲食</rdg></app>甚甘美。因以請王。<note n="0386082" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【三】</note><note n="0386082" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386082"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>往臨。<note n="0386083" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（飲）＋食【三】</note><note n="0386083" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（飲）＋食【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0386083"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飲食</rdg></app>飲食
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0387a" n="0387a"/>
<lb n="0387a01"/><note n="0387001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甘＝甚【三】</note><note n="0387001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">甘＝甚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387001"><lem>甘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">甚</rdg></app>美。<note n="0387002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（王）＋因【三】</note><note n="0387002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（王）＋因【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387002"><lem>因</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王因</rdg></app>問。誰作此食者。<note n="0387003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋臣【三】</note><note n="0387003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大）＋臣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387003"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">大臣</rdg></app>對曰。<note n="0387004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣前賃＝前賃得【三】</note><note n="0387004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣前賃＝前賃得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387004"><lem>臣前
<lb n="0387a02"/>賃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">前賃得</rdg></app>一人能作此食。王遂<note n="0387005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＋（現長生錄）【宋】，（錄）【元】【明】</note><app n="0387005"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">呼現長生錄</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">呼錄</rdg></app>將歸<note n="0387006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宮＝官中【元】，宮中【明】</note><note n="0387006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宮＝官中【元】，＝宮中【明】</note><app n="0387006"><lem>宮</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">官中</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宮中</rdg></app>使作飲
<lb n="0387a03"/>食</p>
<lb n="0387a04"/><p>後日王問長生。汝寧便習兵法不。對曰。實
<lb n="0387a05"/>便習之。<note n="0387007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0387007"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>因取<note n="0387008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【三】</note><note n="0387008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔以〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387008"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0387009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝著【宋】</note><app n="0387009"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>邊而告之曰。我有
<lb n="0387a06"/>怨家。是長壽王子。&M010527;恐行來卒與<note n="0387010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【三】</note><note n="0387010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔我〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387010"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>相逢。
<lb n="0387a07"/>今相恃怙。<note n="0387011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（卿）＋幸【三】</note><note n="0387011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（卿）＋幸【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387011"><lem>幸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">卿幸</rdg></app>相助備之。長生對曰。唯然。
<lb n="0387a08"/>當為大王展力效命。後日<note n="0387012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【三】</note><note n="0387012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387012"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>問長生。汝寧
<lb n="0387a09"/><note n="0387013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好＋（射）【三】</note><note n="0387013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">好＋（射）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387013"><lem>好</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">好射</rdg></app>獵不。對曰。臣<note n="0387014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">少＋（小）【三】</note><note n="0387014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">少＋（小）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387014"><lem>少</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">少小</rdg></app>好獵。王便&CB00330;外嚴駕。
<lb n="0387a10"/>因與長生共<note n="0387015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">出行＝行遊【三】</note><note n="0387015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">出行＝行遊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387015"><lem>出行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">行遊</rdg></app>獵。適入山林便見走獸。
<lb n="0387a11"/>王與長生馳而逐之。轉入深山<note n="0387016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惑＝或【三】</note><note n="0387016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惑＝或【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387016"><lem>惑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">或</rdg></app>失道徑
<lb n="0387a12"/><note n="0387017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不能得出〕－【三】</note><note n="0387017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不能得出〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387017"><lem>不能得出</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。迷惑三<note n="0387018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＋（不得出）【宋】，（不得出路）【元】【明】</note><app n="0387018"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">日不得出</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">日不得出路</rdg></app>。遂至飢困。王<note n="0387019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔因〕－【三】</note><note n="0387019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔因〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387019"><lem>因</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>下
<lb n="0387a13"/>馬解劍以授長生曰。我甚疲極。汝坐我欲枕
<lb n="0387a14"/>汝膝臥。長生言諾。王便得臥。長生自念。我前
<lb n="0387a15"/>後以來求索<note n="0387020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝方【三】</note><note n="0387020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＝方【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387020"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">方</rdg></app>便。今日已得我所願。便拔劍
<lb n="0387a16"/>欲殺貪王。<note n="0387021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">思惟＝念【三】</note><note n="0387021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">思惟＝念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387021"><lem>思惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>我父臨<note n="0387022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">死＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0387022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">死＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387022"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">死之</rdg></app>時囑我<note n="0387023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懇懇＝慇懃【三】</note><note n="0387023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懇懇＝慇懃【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387023"><lem>懇懇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">慇懃</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0387a17"/>奈何快我愚意而違慈父<note n="0387024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕歿之教＝之教非孝之也【三】</note><note n="0387024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕歿之教＝之教非孝之也【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387024"><lem>絕歿之教</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">之教非孝之也</rdg></app>。即內劍
<lb n="0387a18"/>而止。王便驚<note n="0387025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悟＝寤【三】＊</note><note n="0387025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悟＝寤【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0387025"><lem>悟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">寤</rdg></app><note n="0387026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問長生曰＝告曰【三】</note><note n="0387026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">問長生曰＝告曰【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387026"><lem>問長生曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">告曰</rdg></app>。我夢見長壽王
<lb n="0387a19"/>子欲來殺我。我大驚怖。何以如此。長生曰。
<lb n="0387a20"/><note n="0387027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【三】</note><note n="0387027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387027"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>山中有強鬼神見大王在此故來恐怖大
<lb n="0387a21"/>王耳。臣自侍衛。王但安臥無所畏懼也。王<note n="0387028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還得＝即還【三】</note><note n="0387028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還得＝即還【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387028"><lem>
<lb n="0387a22"/>還得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">即還</rdg></app>臥。長生復拔劍欲殺之。重<note n="0387029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔思〕－【三】</note><note n="0387029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔思〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387029"><lem>思</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>憶父言
<lb n="0387a23"/>復止。王復驚<app type="＊" source="0387025"><lem>悟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">寤</rdg></app>。告長生<note n="0387030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝言【三】</note><note n="0387030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰＝言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387030"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>。我<note n="0387031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0387031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔故〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0387031"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0387032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【宋】</note><app n="0387032"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>夢見
<lb n="0387a24"/>長壽王子故欲來殺我。我大畏之。何以爾也。
<lb n="0387a25"/>長生曰。是<app type="＊" source="0387031"><lem>故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>山神所為耳。王無所<note n="0387033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畏＋（懼）【三】</note><note n="0387033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畏＋（懼）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387033"><lem>畏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">畏懼</rdg></app>也。
<lb n="0387a26"/>王復還臥。長生復拔劍欲殺之。思惟父言復
<lb n="0387a27"/>止。遂棄劍於地。無復殺王之意。王復驚<app type="＊" source="0387025"><lem>悟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">寤</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0387a28"/>告長生<app type="＊" source="0386020"><lem>言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曰</rdg></app>。<note n="0387034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0387034"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>復夢見長壽王子自言原<note n="0387035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赦＝意【三】</note><note n="0387035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">赦＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387035"><lem>赦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>
<lb n="0387a29"/>不復殺我。於是長生曰。我即是長壽王太子
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0387b" n="0387b"/>
<lb n="0387b01"/><note n="0387036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">長生＋（也）【三】</note><note n="0387036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">長生＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387036"><lem>長生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">長生也</rdg></app>。我<note n="0387037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實故＝故實【三】</note><note n="0387037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">實故＝故實【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387037"><lem>實故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">故實</rdg></app>來出欲殺大王以報父<note n="0387038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＝&CB00677;耳【三】</note><note n="0387038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨＝&CB00677;耳【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387038"><lem>怨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00677;耳</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0387b02"/>念我父臨<note n="0387039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">死＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0387039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">死＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387039"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">死之</rdg></app>時慇懃囑我。不欲使我報怨。
<lb n="0387b03"/>而我愚癡故<note n="0387040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔欲〕－【三】</note><note n="0387040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔欲〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387040"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>違父之言。詳思父教懇惻慇
<lb n="0387b04"/>懃。不敢違之。是故今投劍於地以順父言。
<lb n="0387b05"/>雖爾猶恐後日迷惑失計而違亡父<note n="0387041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">教也＝之教【三】</note><note n="0387041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教也＝之教【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387041"><lem>教也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">之教</rdg></app>。今
<lb n="0387b06"/>故自告。願大王。便誅伐我身早滅其惡意。可
<lb n="0387b07"/>使終始<note n="0387042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斷絕也＝絕斷【三】</note><note n="0387042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斷絕也＝絕斷【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387042"><lem>斷絕也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">絕斷</rdg></app>。王乃自悔曰。我為兇逆不
<lb n="0387b08"/>別善惡。賢者父子行仁淳固至死不轉。而我
<lb n="0387b09"/>貪酷初不覺知。今日如是命屬子手。子故懷
<lb n="0387b10"/>仁<note n="0387043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惟憶父言〕－【宋】</note><app n="0387043"><lem>惟憶父言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>而不相害。誠感<note n="0387044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厚＝淳【三】</note><note n="0387044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厚＝淳【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387044"><lem>厚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">淳</rdg></app>潤。今欲還
<lb n="0387b11"/>國當從何道<note n="0387045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0387045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387045"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。長生言。我知道徑前故來
<lb n="0387b12"/>者。迷惑大王欲報父<note n="0387046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＝&CB00677;【三】</note><note n="0387046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨＝&CB00677;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387046"><lem>怨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00677;</rdg></app>耳。長生遂與王俱
<lb n="0387b13"/>出林外。便見群臣散滿林際。王便止坐施設
<lb n="0387b14"/>飲食。王問群臣。卿等寧識長壽王子長生不。
<lb n="0387b15"/>中有不識者。對曰不識。中有識者。昔受長
<lb n="0387b16"/>生恩。恐王殺之。亦言不識。王便指示言。是
<lb n="0387b17"/>即長生也。玉曰。從今日始<note n="0387047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝悟【宋】</note><app n="0387047"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">悟</rdg></app>自還<note n="0387048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0387048"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故國。
<lb n="0387b18"/>願以此國還付太子。<note n="0387049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從今日始＝自今以後【三】</note><note n="0387049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從今日始＝自今以後【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387049"><lem>從今日始</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">自今以後</rdg></app>。卿為我弟。
<lb n="0387b19"/>若有他國來相侵奪。當相救助。王遂<note n="0387050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（引）＋率【三】</note><note n="0387050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（引）＋率【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387050"><lem>率</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">引率</rdg></app>臣
<lb n="0387b20"/>兵歸其本國。國有奇<note n="0387051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝珍【三】</note><note n="0387051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">物＝珍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387051"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">珍</rdg></app>更相貢遺</p>
<lb n="0387b21"/><p>佛告諸比丘。時長壽王者<note n="0387052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔今〕－【三】</note><note n="0387052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔今〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387052"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>我身是也。太子
<lb n="0387b22"/>長生者阿難是。貪王者調達是。調達與我世
<lb n="0387b23"/>世有怨。我雖有善意向之。故欲害我。阿難與
<lb n="0387b24"/>之本無惡意。故至相見即有和解之心。菩薩
<lb n="0387b25"/>求道勤苦如是。至見賊害無怨恚之<note n="0387053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝意【三】</note><note n="0387053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387053"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>。<note n="0387054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【三】</note><note n="0387054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔故〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387054"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0387b26"/>自致得佛為三界尊。諸比丘歡喜為佛作禮</p>
<lb n="0387b27"/><lg><note n="0387055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛為海船師…敬受頭面禮〕八十句－【三】</note><note n="0387055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛為海船師…敬受頭面禮〕四百字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0387055" word-count="400"><lem><l>佛為海船師</l><l>法橋度河津</l>
<lb n="0387b28"/><l>大乘道之輿</l><l>一切度天人</l>
<lb n="0387b29"/><l>亦謂自解結</l><l>度岸得昇仙</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0387c" n="0387c"/>
<lb n="0387c01"/><l>都使諸弟子</l><l>縛解至泥洹</l>
<lb n="0387c02"/><l>敬謁法王來</l><l>心正道力安</l>
<lb n="0387c03"/><l>最勝號為佛</l><l>名顯若雪山</l>
<lb n="0387c04"/><l>譬華淨無疑</l><l>得喜如近香</l>
<lb n="0387c05"/><l>萬身觀無厭</l><l>光若靈曜明</l>
<lb n="0387c06"/><l>八正覺自得</l><l>無離無所染</l>
<lb n="0387c07"/><l>愛盡破欲網</l><l>自然無師受</l>
<lb n="0387c08"/><l>我行無師保</l><l>志獨無等侶</l>
<lb n="0387c09"/><l>積一得作佛</l><l>從是通聖道</l>
<lb n="0387c10"/><l>至道無往返</l><l>玄微清妙真</l>
<lb n="0387c11"/><l>不歿不復生</l><l>是處為泥洹</l>
<lb n="0387c12"/><l>此要寂無上</l><l>畢竟不受辛</l>
<lb n="0387c13"/><l>雖天有善處</l><l>皆莫如泥洹</l>
<lb n="0387c14"/><l>吾師天中天</l><l>三界無極尊</l>
<lb n="0387c15"/><l>相好身丈六</l><l>神通遊虛空</l>
<lb n="0387c16"/><l>華薰去五陰</l><l>拔斷十二根</l>
<lb n="0387c17"/><l>不貪天世位</l><l>心淨開法門</l>
<lb n="0387c18"/><l>佛為無上法</l><l>道御清等行</l>
<lb n="0387c19"/><l>三寶於後世</l><l>絕滅諸欲情</l>
<lb n="0387c20"/><l>離苦勝無為</l><l>常樂快安寧</l>
<lb n="0387c21"/><l>願常會佛前</l><l>等度諸群生</l>
<lb n="0387c22"/><l>佛所本行願</l><l>精進百劫勤</l>
<lb n="0387c23"/><l>四等大布施</l><l>十方受弘恩</l>
<lb n="0387c24"/><l>持戒淨無垢</l><l>慈柔護眾生</l>
<lb n="0387c25"/><l>用慧入禪定</l><l>大悲普讀經</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0161.0388a" n="0388a"/>
<lb n="0388a01"/><l>常為智所仰</l><l>眾聖所共宗</l>
<lb n="0388a02"/><l>釋梵以為師</l><l>乃知佛為尊</l>
<lb n="0388a03"/><l>難值無有比</l><l>最上無過者</l>
<lb n="0388a04"/><l>功德以流布</l><l>當為稽首禮</l>
<lb n="0388a05"/><l>聽我歌十方</l><l>棄蓋寂定禪</l>
<lb n="0388a06"/><l>光徹照七天</l><l>德香殊栴檀</l>
<lb n="0388a07"/><l>上帝神妙來</l><l>歎仰欲見尊</l>
<lb n="0388a08"/><l>釋梵齊敬意</l><l>稽首欲受問</l>
<lb n="0388a09"/><l>所以佛度世</l><l>福施以周匝</l>
<lb n="0388a10"/><l>所說教戒行</l><l>在在悉分明</l>
<lb n="0388a11"/><l>亦以法流布</l><l>弟子樂受行</l>
<lb n="0388a12"/><l>令天人鬼龍</l><l>敬受頭面禮</l></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lg>
<lb n="0388a13"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0388001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋長【元】【明】</note><app n="0388001"><lem>長</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說長</rdg></app>壽王經</jhead></juan></div1>
